# {{ name }}

This repository defines an AWS security group using the platform Terraform module.

## Inputs

- Environment: `{{ environment }}`
- AWS region: `{{ aws_region }}`
- AWS account: `{{ aws_account_id }}`
- VPC ID: `{{ vpc_id }}`
- Owner: `{{ owner }}`
- Project: `{{ project }}`

## Usage

```bash
terraform init
terraform fmt -check
terraform validate
terraform plan
```

Before applying, review each ingress and egress rule for least privilege. The module rejects empty rule sources and unrestricted ingress CIDRs.
